name: Tersambung
description: In life, in death, in commotion, crowds, loneliness, hope, despair. Between seconds, hours, days can not be separated from the music. In making works that are always accompanied by music, accompanying music on the way, sharing energy through the exchange of references to listening to music. Until as a reminder of the history of someone's journey. Everything that is connected is at the base of the rhythmic space that connects
